UML:TaggedValue.value: This file defines a set of standard POSC units of measure for various quantity classes. This units list captures information contained in the POSC units dictionary at http://www.posc.org/refs/poscUnits20.xml. The enumerated lists do not contain any deprecated units.
The units of measure that are valid for measured depths in a wellbore.
The units of measure that are valid for vertical gravity based coordinates (i.e., elevation or vertical depth) within the context of a well.
